\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}\cos(\frac{2\pi k}{n})=Re\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}e^{i2\pi k/n}= Re\left\{\frac{1-e^{i2\pi n/n}}{1-e^{i2\pi/n}}\right\}=0,\quad n>1
